+### ALFRED-BP-015 — Use readiness, lane, and hard flags as controls, not scores
+
+```yaml
+id: ALFRED-BP-015
+status: accepted
+practice: Record readiness, lane, and hard flags as routing controls for process handovers.
+context_conditions:
